{{Campaignbox Yemeni Crisis}}
2015年12月6日，[[亞丁|亚丁]]市长贾法尔·穆罕默德·萨阿德[[少将|少将]]及其随行人员因一场汽车炸弹袭击身亡。萨阿德当时正前往他在亚丁西部地区的办公室。<ref name="Independent">{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/yemen-governor-killed-in-suicide-car-bombing-a6762116.html|title=Yemen governor killed in Isis-claimed 'car bombing'|work=Independent New Agency|date=2015-12-06|accessdate=2015-12-08|author=Osborne, Samuel|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223042918/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/yemen-governor-killed-in-suicide-car-bombing-a6762116.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Al Arabiya">{{Cite news|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/12/06/Yemen-s-Aden-governor-killed-in-RPG-attack-.html|title=ISIS claims killing of Aden governor in Yemen|work=Al Arabiya News|date=2015-12-06|accessdate=2015-12-08|author=Staff writer of Al Arabiya News|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210015542/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/12/06/Yemen-s-Aden-governor-killed-in-RPG-attack-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://europe.newsweek.com/islamic-state-claim-responsibility-car-bomb-killing-yemen-governor-401652?rm=eu|title=Islamic State Claims Responsibility After Yemen Official Killed by Car Bomb|work=Europe.Newsweek|date=2015-12-06|accessdate=2015-12-08|author=Westcott, Lucy|archive-date=2020-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314223237/https://www.newsweek.com/islamic-state-claim-responsibility-car-bomb-killing-yemen-governor-401652|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[伊斯兰国|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国]]也门分支声称对袭击负责。<ref name="reuters">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-governor-idUSKBN0TP05K20151206#XsEZUMtADQdasr31.97|title=Yemen's Aden governor killed in car bombing claimed by Islamic State|work=Reuters|date=2015-12-06|accessdate=2015-12-08|author=Mukhashaf, Mohammed|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323142134/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-governor-idUSKBN0TP05K20151206#XsEZUMtADQdasr31.97|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Independent"/><ref name="Al Arabiya"/>他们说萨阿德是压迫者，是异教徒，并威胁要在也门进行进一步的袭击。该组织表示，当萨阿德的车队经过停放汽车的地方时，他们引爆了炸弹。

爆炸声在距离10公里远的地方也能听到。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://triblive.com/usworld/world/9580002-74/explosion-islamic-state#axzz3tiC0PadH|title=kills Yemen governor, bodyguards in Aden|work=Triblive|date=2015-12-06|accessdate=2015-12-08|author=The Associated Press|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222190654/http://triblive.com/usworld/world/9580002-74/explosion-islamic-state#axzz3tiC0PadH|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters"/>萨阿德的六名保镖被炸死，另有数人受伤。医务人员表示受害者的尸体无法辨认。<ref name="Al Arabiya"/>

伊斯兰国通过亚丁-阿比扬省的媒体发布了一段录像，其中包含此次事件的画面。

